@startuml timing
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
' Diagrama de tiempos (UML) — respuesta del control on/off con histeresis (banda muerta).
title Respuesta del control con histeresis

robust "Temperatura" as T
binary "Cooler (relay)" as C

@0
T is "< tempMax"
C is low
@2
T is "sube -> tempMax"
@3
T is ">= tempMax"
C is high
@5
T is "baja (> tempMax - hist)"
@7
T is "<= tempMax - hist"
C is low
@9
T is "< tempMax"

highlight 3 to 7 #Silver;line:Black : cooler ON (banda muerta)
@enduml
